"},{"pid":"e46320725769b3d76d8dbeefca4474445bf204f1","tid":2514304,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本就係想判同佢哋終生監禁先至安樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b4f163daae410e234f9a909610a30e4b63721187","tid":2514304,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:52:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本就係想判佢哋終生監禁先至安樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1857cbd24b80c0415ca2cd79b485c4c1054699ea","tid":2514304,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:53:40.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9920e232f581a9550c42b19d1ebbbec1155661ee","tid":2514304,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:00:40.000Z","msg":"控方申請將 D3的$30000 D4的$8000 D6的$10000 保釋金充公，辯方就此沒有陳詞，控方申請獲批。"},{"pid":"c06ae689ef4dd638a1bc6f2c1f4dee16b4265df9","tid":2514304,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:03:34.000Z","msg":"12港人案中的10人早前刑滿先後移交香港，當中張俊富、張銘裕及嚴文謙的案件今於東區法院法院再訊。張俊富被加控管有爆炸品及無牌管有槍械兩罪，另一項僅針對其的管有攻擊性武器及其他適合作非法用途的工具則獲撤銷。主任裁判官羅德泉將案件押後至6月7日作提訊日，各被告還押懲教看管。<br />\n<br />\n張俊富今被加控管有爆炸品及無牌管有槍械兩罪，指其在2019年12月3日至12月8日，在荃灣致利大廈一單位內與黃振強管有兩盒煙花；並於同年12月8日在同地管有買罐裝有諾香草胺的噴霧器。"},{"pid":"69f8343380d6ae7004c0d1a889e558dcb50ceeab","tid":2514304,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93ab56edf5bcbf031fe62de987b883f761fa41e","tid":2514304,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit